name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-santa-rosa-reef-2003
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 2 sites at Santa Rosa Reef in the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands (CNMI) in September, 2003 from the NOAA vessel Oscar Elton Sette (OES03-07). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
